1️⃣ Entitlement Request:-
Entitlement = Permission / Access
Example:-
AD Group
SAP Role
Database Access
Jira Permission
Entitlement Request = kisi user ko permission dena ya remove karna

Example:-
AttributeRequest entitlement = new AttributeRequest();
entitlement.setName("memberOf");
entitlement.setValue("Finance_Group");
entitlement.setOperation(ProvisioningPlan.Operation.Add);

Matlab:-
User ko Finance_Group access do

2️⃣ AccountRequest:-
AccountRequest = Application account par kya operation karna hai

Ye batata hai:-
Account create karna
Account delete karna
Account update karna

Example:-
AccountRequest accReq = new AccountRequest();
accReq.setApplication("ActiveDirectory");
accReq.setOperation(AccountRequest.Operation.Create);

Matlab:-
Active Directory me new account create karo.

3️⃣ AttributeRequest:-
AttributeRequest = Account ke andar ka attribute change karna

Account ke andar attributes hote hain:-
username
department
role
email

Example:-
AttributeRequest attrReq = new AttributeRequest();
attrReq.setName("department");
attrReq.setValue("Finance");
Matlab:-
User ka department Finance set karo.

()Code Structure:-
ProvisioningPlan plan = new ProvisioningPlan();

AccountRequest accReq = new AccountRequest();
accReq.setApplication("ActiveDirectory");
accReq.setOperation(AccountRequest.Operation.Create);

AttributeRequest attrReq = new AttributeRequest();
attrReq.setName("department");
attrReq.setValue("Finance");

AttributeRequest entitlement = new AttributeRequest();
entitlement.setName("memberOf");
entitlement.setValue("Finance_Group");

accReq.add(attrReq);
accReq.add(entitlement);

plan.add(accReq);